WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.389
Hey, good morning family. Thank you for

00:00:02.399 --> 00:00:04.630
joining me today. Well, there is a lot

00:00:04.640 --> 00:00:06.110
going on, isn't

00:00:06.120 --> 00:00:09.430
there? The whole Trump tariff

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:11.910
thing is really shaking some

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:14.709
things up, stirring some things up, and

00:00:14.719 --> 00:00:17.189
people ask, "Brandon,"through

00:00:17.189 --> 00:00:17.199
emails and

00:00:17.199 --> 00:00:20.230
through wherever

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:22.630
they are. It's been

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:25.670
amazing. People are freaked out and

00:00:25.670 --> 00:00:25.680
asking,

00:00:25.680 --> 00:00:28.790
"Should we store food? Should we buy

00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:30.790
water? Should we buy guns? Should we do

00:00:30.790 --> 00:00:30.800
this?"Listen,

00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:34.310
you should not do anything

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:38.229
by watching a video. What you should do

00:00:38.239 --> 00:00:41.830
is pray and ask the Holy Spirit what you

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:44.470
should do for your finances and for your

00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:48.110
life. I told you all I

00:00:48.120 --> 00:00:52.069
hear in part and I see in part. When

00:00:52.079 --> 00:00:54.950
the things that I see start coming up in

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:57.750
the news, I bring the old videos out

00:00:57.760 --> 00:00:59.510
because I have so many trolls saying

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:01.270
that I'm making stuff up, and

00:01:01.280 --> 00:01:03.430
so I'm just showing, "Hey, I do see

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:05.509
stuff and the Lord's showing me these

00:01:05.509 --> 00:01:05.519
things."And

00:01:05.519 --> 00:01:07.590
they say, "Are you a

00:01:07.590 --> 00:01:07.600
prophet?"I

00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:11.429
say, "No, I'm not a prophet. I'm a

00:01:11.429 --> 00:01:11.439
watchman."I've

00:01:11.439 --> 00:01:13.030
told you all

00:01:13.040 --> 00:01:16.149
this. I'm called to pray. And I

00:01:16.159 --> 00:01:18.950
believe the Lord shows me as a watchman

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:22.390
on the wall,

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:24.950
looking out on a horizon seeing what's coming

00:01:24.960 --> 00:01:27.350
towards the camp. "Hey, this is what I

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:29.149
see

00:01:29.149 --> 00:01:29.159
coming."And

00:01:29.159 --> 00:01:32.390
so far there's a lot of accuracy.

00:01:32.390 --> 00:01:32.400
Have

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:35.190
a

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:37.190
lot of the things I've seen not come to

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:38.710
pass? Yes, there's a lot of things that

00:01:38.720 --> 00:01:40.550
I've seen that have not come to

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:42.830
pass yet. But the things that I've told

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:45.749
you so far—some of those things you've

00:01:45.759 --> 00:01:48.069
seen in the news. So they go,

00:01:48.079 --> 00:01:51.270
"Well, what's this mean

00:01:51.270 --> 00:01:51.280
now?"Honestly,

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:54.310
I pray none of this that

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:57.030
I've seen comes to pass. And you can

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:58.550
point fingers at me, call me false all

00:01:58.560 --> 00:02:00.789
day long, and say he's

00:02:00.799 --> 00:02:02.870
making stuff up or whatever, but I'm

00:02:02.880 --> 00:02:06.789
here to tell you, we have to pray for

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:08.710
what I've seen about China and the

00:02:08.720 --> 00:02:12.830
trade

00:02:12.840 --> 00:02:16.229
wars because it's about medical.

00:02:16.239 --> 00:02:19.190
They get so irritated and

00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:21.110
so frustrated with the escalation of

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:23.190
this that they start saying, "We're not

00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:25.670
giving you medicines and

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:28.150
things like that."That's what I saw.

00:02:28.160 --> 00:02:29.589
Now, is that for you to get scared

00:02:29.599 --> 00:02:33.910
about? No. It could not happen.

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:36.869
If we pray and we ask the Father

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:40.309
to intervene in this and pray for these

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:43.750
trade wars to deescalate and fall apart

00:02:43.760 --> 00:02:45.830
and that they come to an agreement, then

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:48.309
it's all over. Wouldn't it be? I mean,

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:49.670
the

00:02:49.680 --> 00:02:52.150
ultimate goal is not for this to keep

00:02:52.160 --> 00:02:53.589
going and going and getting out of

00:02:53.599 --> 00:02:56.869
control and then we go, "Oh,

00:02:56.869 --> 00:02:56.879
no."Everything

00:02:56.879 --> 00:02:59.470
I told you—I saw

00:02:59.480 --> 00:03:01.750
stores that were not able to get

00:03:01.760 --> 00:03:04.149
merchandise back and forth throughout

00:03:04.159 --> 00:03:06.070
all the Targets and all the Walmarts and

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:08.790
all the Costcos and the Sam's Clubs, and

00:03:08.800 --> 00:03:10.470
that they had to take everything out of

00:03:10.480 --> 00:03:12.149
one store and put it in another store

00:03:12.159 --> 00:03:13.990
because they had to shut that store down

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:17.509
because they couldn't get the supplies.

00:03:17.519 --> 00:03:20.390
The things I see, if you look at it in

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:23.430
the natural, it will scare you. It will

00:03:23.440 --> 00:03:25.750
really freak you out. But if you keep

00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:28.949
your eyes on Him, if you keep your eyes

00:03:28.959 --> 00:03:31.509
vertical and you keep looking at the

00:03:31.519 --> 00:03:33.589
Father and praying over this stuff,

00:03:33.599 --> 00:03:36.149
knowing that we have authority, it

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:37.830
shouldn't freak you out. Now, I have a

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:39.750
lot of people all freaked out, and my

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:41.750
job right now is I'm

00:03:41.760 --> 00:03:44.949
diffusing it to say, "Listen, the sky's

00:03:44.959 --> 00:03:47.830
not falling."Yes, I saw this. Yes, what

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:50.229
I saw about the trade wars and the

00:03:50.239 --> 00:03:53.030
things coming. We should pray.

00:03:53.040 --> 00:03:55.830
That's what we're here to do. So,

00:03:55.840 --> 00:03:57.589
can we change it through prayer? I

00:03:57.599 --> 00:04:00.309
believe so. All things are possible to

00:04:00.319 --> 00:04:02.630
him who believes. I believe that every

00:04:02.640 --> 00:04:04.869
believer has the authority of the

00:04:04.879 --> 00:04:06.550
believer inside of him. We have the

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:08.149
power and authority that Jesus has given

00:04:08.159 --> 00:04:11.750
us. That as He is, so are we

00:04:11.760 --> 00:04:14.869
in this world. And if Jesus can cause

00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:16.789
peace to the storms, we can call peace

00:04:16.799 --> 00:04:19.590
to the storms. We are made in the image

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:21.749
of God and we are joint heirs of Jesus

00:04:21.759 --> 00:04:23.510
Christ. And I believe that we can do

00:04:23.520 --> 00:04:25.030
those things. Some people don't believe

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:27.430
it, but I believe we do. So if you want

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:29.270
to watch me, fine. If you don't want

00:04:29.280 --> 00:04:30.629
to agree with it, that's on

00:04:30.639 --> 00:04:31.990
you. I know I have all kinds of

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:33.350
different beliefs, but I want to tell

00:04:33.360 --> 00:04:35.670
you this. People ask, "Brandon, what

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:37.270
are you doing right now? Are you storing

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:40.150
up food? Are you doing all

00:04:40.150 --> 00:04:40.160
this?"No,

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:43.189
I'm not. I am not getting in fear

00:04:43.199 --> 00:04:44.790
and going out to the grocery store and

00:04:44.800 --> 00:04:46.790
buying $10,000 worth of groceries and

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:48.230
going, "Well, I've got it all in the

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:49.830
garage, and I've got it out here and it's

00:04:49.840 --> 00:04:51.189
going to get hot in the summer and

00:04:51.199 --> 00:04:53.350
then next thing I know it's

00:04:53.350 --> 00:04:53.360
spoiled."I'm

00:04:53.360 --> 00:04:55.110
not doing that. The Holy Spirit

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:57.189
didn't tell me, "Brandon, you should

00:04:57.199 --> 00:05:01.030
go out and buy a freezer full of meat at

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:03.629
Sam's

00:05:03.629 --> 00:05:03.639
tomorrow."He

00:05:03.639 --> 00:05:07.110
may tell you to do that; He may

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:09.590
not. But you have to just follow Him for

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:12.070
your

00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:14.710
household. He may say to you,

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:16.870
"Go get water. Go get this. Go get

00:05:16.870 --> 00:05:16.880
that."I

00:05:16.880 --> 00:05:19.189
don't know

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:20.950
where you live. I don't know if you live

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:23.590
in a major apartment complex with

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:26.390
500 people around

00:05:26.390 --> 00:05:26.400
you—I

00:05:26.400 --> 00:05:28.870
have no idea, folks. If I lived in

00:05:28.880 --> 00:05:31.590
Orlando or if I lived in Tampa or a

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:33.990
major city that I saw all those people

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:36.390
and it's so packed full of people, I

00:05:36.400 --> 00:05:38.790
might have four or five days'worth of

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:41.270
extra food.

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:43.990
I live in a little bitty town

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:46.390
with not a lot of people and

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:48.870
a lot around us is farmers—a lot of farmers and a lot of

00:05:48.880 --> 00:05:51.189
people growing

00:05:51.199 --> 00:05:53.670
tomato plants and squash in the summer.

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:55.350
I can go down to the local

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:57.670
farmers market and stock up every

00:05:57.680 --> 00:05:59.749
single week and get fresh vegetables

00:05:59.759 --> 00:06:02.629
around here with

00:06:02.629 --> 00:06:02.639
apples—not

00:06:02.639 --> 00:06:04.870
oranges, but apples—and peaches and

00:06:04.880 --> 00:06:07.830
pears in the fall and toward the late

00:06:07.840 --> 00:06:09.909
summer. There's all kinds of stuff

00:06:09.919 --> 00:06:11.830
around here. So, am I freaked out about

00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:13.350
food? No. There's tons of food around

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:15.510
here; we have farmers everywhere. Now,

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:17.189
if I lived in Chicago, it might be a

00:06:17.199 --> 00:06:19.029
different story. I don't know. But I

00:06:19.039 --> 00:06:21.749
have to tell you, am I afraid? People

00:06:21.759 --> 00:06:23.270
said, "Should I pull my money out of my

00:06:23.270 --> 00:06:23.280
bank?"I

00:06:23.280 --> 00:06:25.749
don't know what you should do.

00:06:25.759 --> 00:06:28.070
All I saw was the things I

00:06:28.080 --> 00:06:30.390
see and I relay it and I tell you what

00:06:30.400 --> 00:06:32.469
I see. Is that for you? That's for you

00:06:32.479 --> 00:06:34.629
to pray about. I do not want this stuff

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:37.189
I see to come to pass. It's like people

00:06:37.199 --> 00:06:39.670
go, "Well, good for you, Brandon.

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:41.430
It came to pass."No, that means

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:45.270
it's a prayer fail. In my opinion, if I

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:47.909
see something that's drastic and I come

00:06:47.919 --> 00:06:49.909
on here and tell you about it and it

00:06:49.919 --> 00:06:51.390
happens, we

00:06:51.400 --> 00:06:53.990
failed. Now, I know some of the things

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.909
we can stop and some of the

00:06:55.919 --> 00:06:58.150
things we can't. I know we are

00:07:01.199 --> 00:07:02.870
in the last of the last days and I

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:05.510
told you we're going to see major things

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:07.909
coming, but some of the things I believe

00:07:07.919 --> 00:07:11.270
we can stop. And so that's

00:07:11.280 --> 00:07:15.029
my main job: to always

00:07:15.039 --> 00:07:17.189
pray and ask the Father to change it,

00:07:18.440 --> 00:07:21.029
just like Abraham. He came and

00:07:21.039 --> 00:07:24.150
He told Abraham what He was going to do

00:07:24.160 --> 00:07:26.710
and they had a conversation about it.

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:29.589
And if you are a friend of God and you

00:07:29.599 --> 00:07:31.670
are joint heirs with Him and He comes

00:07:31.680 --> 00:07:33.990
and talks to you, He'll tell you what

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:36.510
He's going to do before He does

00:07:36.520 --> 00:07:38.990
it. Just because we're

00:07:38.990 --> 00:07:39.000
friends—you

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:41.430
tell your wife everything,

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:43.110
don't you? Usually, if you have a good

00:07:43.120 --> 00:07:45.189
marriage, or your wife tells her husband

00:07:45.199 --> 00:07:47.830
everything, right? So, the

00:07:47.840 --> 00:07:50.230
Father, it's like a marriage; we

00:07:50.240 --> 00:07:52.550
talk and we're friends. And so, that's

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:54.629
the way I look at it every day. I just

00:07:54.639 --> 00:07:56.790
go, "Hey, Lord, what's going on

00:07:56.790 --> 00:07:56.800
today?"Just

00:07:56.800 --> 00:07:58.869
like I did with New Orleans

00:07:58.879 --> 00:08:01.309
and the shooting or Trump's

00:08:01.319 --> 00:08:04.469
ear, the economy crashing afterwards.

00:08:04.479 --> 00:08:07.189
We're seeing those things. It's

00:08:07.199 --> 00:08:09.430
happening. Do I believe we have a window

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:11.629
still? People ask, "Brandon, you said we had a

00:08:11.639 --> 00:08:14.390
window. You said we had a window of four

00:08:14.400 --> 00:08:16.589
years. Where'd that four years go,

00:08:16.589 --> 00:08:16.599
buddy?"This

00:08:16.599 --> 00:08:19.350
is what I want to

00:08:19.360 --> 00:08:21.909
say back to you: it's a four-year window

00:08:21.919 --> 00:08:24.070
of grace. I believe at the end of

00:08:24.070 --> 00:08:24.080
that

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:25.990
four-year window—I don't know, because

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:27.749
I'm not going to assume, add to, or take

00:08:27.759 --> 00:08:29.670
away from anything that He's saying—but

00:08:29.670 --> 00:08:29.680
a

00:08:29.680 --> 00:08:31.749
four-year

00:08:31.759 --> 00:08:33.670
window to me is a four-year window

00:08:33.680 --> 00:08:35.990
before He comes. That's what I have in

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:37.990
my heart: that He's getting ready to come

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:41.110
that quickly. He said it's one last call,

00:08:41.120 --> 00:08:42.949
and He's leaving the ninety-nine to go after the one. He's looking for the

00:08:42.949 --> 00:08:42.959
sinner

00:08:42.959 --> 00:08:45.430
in

00:08:45.430 --> 00:08:45.440
the

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:47.670
way-back

00:08:47.680 --> 00:08:49.670
fields. That's

00:08:49.680 --> 00:08:51.829
what He's after right now. How long does

00:08:51.839 --> 00:08:53.750
it take to get all those in? I have no

00:08:53.760 --> 00:08:55.190
idea. People are like, 'We need to get

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:57.750
out of here right now.'Listen, North

00:08:57.760 --> 00:09:00.470
Korea has not been

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:03.590
evangelized yet. Has North Korea

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:07.670
been radically taught the word of

00:09:07.680 --> 00:09:09.910
God? My

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:11.829
son told me there's 40-some million people

00:09:11.839 --> 00:09:13.829
in North Korea that have never

00:09:13.829 --> 00:09:13.839
heard—a

00:09:13.839 --> 00:09:15.870
lot of them have never heard the

00:09:15.880 --> 00:09:19.430
gospel. Is that fair? No, that's not

00:09:19.440 --> 00:09:21.750
fair. There's a lot of people in China

00:09:21.760 --> 00:09:23.590
that are still so bound because they're

00:09:23.600 --> 00:09:25.350
underneath the Iron Curtain that they

00:09:25.360 --> 00:09:27.750
have not heard yet, and Vietnam and all

00:09:27.760 --> 00:09:29.190
these other places. There's a lot of

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:31.910
people that have not had the opportunity

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:34.790
to hear the gospel. I know that the Lord

00:09:34.800 --> 00:09:36.710
is the Lord of the harvest, and His

00:09:36.720 --> 00:09:38.990
heart is for the souls. His heart is the

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:42.150
harvest.

00:09:42.160 --> 00:09:43.670
Regardless of what everybody

00:09:43.670 --> 00:09:43.680
wants—to

00:09:43.680 --> 00:09:45.269
go, 'Well, I'm tired. I'm ready to get

00:09:45.279 --> 00:09:48.550
out of here'—listen, I want to occupy

00:09:48.560 --> 00:09:51.269
until He comes. So, the four-year window

00:09:51.279 --> 00:09:54.310
to me is an extension of grace. Will we

00:09:54.320 --> 00:09:57.670
still see birthing pains? Yes. I'm

00:09:57.670 --> 00:09:57.680
believing—and

00:09:57.680 --> 00:09:59.829
I told you all I believe

00:09:59.839 --> 00:10:01.910
when I've prayed and I've heard the

00:10:01.910 --> 00:10:01.920
Lord—that

00:10:01.920 --> 00:10:04.430
we will have a wealth

00:10:04.440 --> 00:10:07.110
transfer laid up for the righteous.

00:10:07.120 --> 00:10:09.269
If you're listening, not everybody's

00:10:09.279 --> 00:10:10.870
going to participate in this. Oh, I

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:13.110
don't know. I pray I do. Honest to

00:10:13.120 --> 00:10:15.350
goodness, you all. Am I qualified for

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:17.590
it? I don't know. I pray and I ask Him,

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:20.870
'Father, make me right before You that I

00:10:20.880 --> 00:10:23.590
would be able to be used by You. That if

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:25.110
You want to give me an idea to get

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:27.910
wealth, then Father, to help bring forth

00:10:27.920 --> 00:10:29.910
the gospel, to do something for Your

00:10:29.920 --> 00:10:32.350
kingdom, to support people, to help

00:10:32.360 --> 00:10:36.310
them, then Father, search me and

00:10:36.320 --> 00:10:39.110
know me.'If I'm not qualified and I mess

00:10:39.120 --> 00:10:41.030
up, Father, then if it's going to cost

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:43.190
me my salvation, if this is going to

00:10:43.200 --> 00:10:45.190
cost me my marriage, if this is going to

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:47.590
cost me my children and we can't handle

00:10:47.600 --> 00:10:50.310
it, then by all means, Lord, remove that

00:10:50.320 --> 00:10:53.110
from me because I would rather

00:10:53.120 --> 00:10:55.389
have nothing than lose my

00:10:55.399 --> 00:10:59.910
soul to money, to mammon. But if He can

00:10:59.920 --> 00:11:02.350
trust me and He can look at me and say,

00:11:02.360 --> 00:11:05.910
'Brandon, okay.'And He said, 'You

00:11:05.920 --> 00:11:07.509
may not be able to handle a billion

00:11:07.519 --> 00:11:10.389
dollars, son, or a million dollars. I'll

00:11:10.399 --> 00:11:13.350
give you this.'I don't know. All I know

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:16.470
is I seek Him. And as I seek Him, I will

00:11:16.480 --> 00:11:18.870
find Him. The Bible says that, and all

00:11:18.880 --> 00:11:20.710
the other stuff will be added unto me as

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:23.350
I seek Him. And if He sees that I can

00:11:23.360 --> 00:11:25.030
handle it, fine. And if He says,

00:11:25.040 --> 00:11:27.269
'Brandon, I need you to plant a big

00:11:27.279 --> 00:11:29.190
garden this summer

00:11:29.200 --> 00:11:31.269
in the next couple of days'—I mean, He

00:11:31.279 --> 00:11:32.949
may tell me. I don't know. I'll go out

00:11:32.959 --> 00:11:36.069
there and say, 'Braden, let's go outside

00:11:36.079 --> 00:11:38.389
and get the ground till up.'I mean,

00:11:38.399 --> 00:11:41.670
that's what we'll do. I just obey Him.

00:11:41.680 --> 00:11:44.150
And He may say, 'Brandon,

00:11:44.160 --> 00:11:46.949
you need to have some cash on hand. You

00:11:46.959 --> 00:11:49.750
may need to have some

00:11:49.760 --> 00:11:52.310
ones on hand or some fives or some tens

00:11:52.320 --> 00:11:55.030
or twenties.'I don't know. Whatever He tells

00:11:55.040 --> 00:11:57.389
you to do, do it. I was thinking about

00:11:57.399 --> 00:12:03.350
when Mary pulled on Jesus and

00:12:03.360 --> 00:12:05.030
she was putting a mandate on that

00:12:05.040 --> 00:12:08.430
anointing on His life before it was

00:12:08.440 --> 00:12:11.629
time. And she went to Him and she said,

00:12:11.639 --> 00:12:14.069
'Jesus, will you help the bride and

00:12:14.079 --> 00:12:17.990
bridegroom

00:12:18.000 --> 00:12:19.910
make the wine? Can you

00:12:19.920 --> 00:12:23.110
help him?'Basically, so He

00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:25.750
said, 'It's not My time yet.'But her

00:12:25.760 --> 00:12:27.910
putting a mandate on that anointing that

00:12:27.920 --> 00:12:30.310
was on His life, knowing who He was,

00:12:30.320 --> 00:12:32.710
brought it forth and He started walking

00:12:32.720 --> 00:12:35.509
in it. It's putting a

00:12:35.519 --> 00:12:38.790
demand on the anointing

00:12:38.800 --> 00:12:42.230
that brings forth the giftings.

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:44.870
Look what happened

00:12:44.880 --> 00:12:48.310
to that feast: Jesus

00:12:48.320 --> 00:12:50.710
showed up and He showed off. And I

00:12:50.720 --> 00:12:52.710
believe as we put a demand on it:

00:12:52.720 --> 00:12:55.670
'Father, You are our provider. You're

00:12:55.680 --> 00:12:59.350
Jehovah Jireh.'I believe that You take

00:12:59.360 --> 00:13:01.350
care of the lilies of the field and the

00:13:01.360 --> 00:13:03.750
birds of the air. How much more will You

00:13:03.760 --> 00:13:06.069
take care of me as you put a demand on

00:13:06.079 --> 00:13:09.190
it? If He took care of water and turned

00:13:09.200 --> 00:13:11.430
it into wine, how much more

00:13:11.440 --> 00:13:13.509
will He? We don't need a drink;

00:13:13.519 --> 00:13:17.310
maybe all I need is some

00:13:17.320 --> 00:13:19.750
groceries.

00:13:19.760 --> 00:13:22.069
If Mary

00:13:22.079 --> 00:13:25.430
could put a mandate on the anointing and

00:13:25.440 --> 00:13:29.030
pull, and know and believe and

00:13:29.040 --> 00:13:31.430
stretch out her voice to Him as a

00:13:31.440 --> 00:13:35.150
mother and say, 'I know You can. Will

00:13:35.160 --> 00:13:38.230
You? Thank you for doing

00:13:38.230 --> 00:13:38.240
this'—and

00:13:38.240 --> 00:13:41.430
He's like, 'Out of compassion.'If He

00:13:41.440 --> 00:13:44.150
had compassion for them, how much more

00:13:44.160 --> 00:13:45.949
will He have compassion for

00:13:45.959 --> 00:13:51.509
you? Will you just trust Him and say, 'I

00:13:51.519 --> 00:13:52.550
believe You're going to take care of me

00:13:52.560 --> 00:13:56.230
in these end times regardless of what I

00:13:56.240 --> 00:13:59.110
see on the stock market'? Regardless of

00:13:59.120 --> 00:14:02.230
what I see with tariffs, if the

00:14:02.240 --> 00:14:04.590
Lord tells you to

00:14:04.590 --> 00:14:04.600
do—remember

00:14:04.600 --> 00:14:07.030
what Mary turned to the servants and

00:14:07.040 --> 00:14:10.189
said, 'Whatever He tells you to do, do

00:14:10.189 --> 00:14:10.199
it.'It

00:14:10.199 --> 00:14:12.790
was an act of obedience

00:14:12.800 --> 00:14:15.590
immediately to go and bring forth as

00:14:15.600 --> 00:14:17.670
she was pulling on it and putting a

00:14:17.680 --> 00:14:21.509
mandate on it and saying, 'Help

00:14:21.509 --> 00:14:21.519
us.'Then

00:14:21.519 --> 00:14:24.150
it was obedience to what He

00:14:24.160 --> 00:14:26.470
instructed to bring it to pass of what

00:14:26.480 --> 00:14:27.949
they were believing

00:14:27.959 --> 00:14:32.069
for. And here the wine came and God

00:14:32.079 --> 00:14:33.910
showed up and showed off. But it was

00:14:33.920 --> 00:14:36.470
obedience. So as we put a mandate on it:

00:14:36.480 --> 00:14:38.310
'Father, You're going to take care of

00:14:38.310 --> 00:14:38.320
us.'I

00:14:38.320 --> 00:14:39.629
believe

00:14:39.639 --> 00:14:42.870
it. You've got my life. I'm

00:14:42.880 --> 00:14:44.069
not going to stress out and worry about

00:14:44.079 --> 00:14:46.629
any of this. But if He speaks to you and

00:14:46.639 --> 00:14:50.389
He says, 'All right, I know I'm

00:14:50.399 --> 00:14:51.430
going to take care of you, but I want

00:14:51.440 --> 00:14:53.550
you to go down and put the water in the

00:14:53.550 --> 00:14:53.560
jugs,'and

00:14:53.560 --> 00:14:56.389
you say, 'Well, I thought You

00:14:56.389 --> 00:14:56.399
were

00:14:56.399 --> 00:14:57.590
just going to show up and show off and

00:14:57.600 --> 00:14:58.750
do

00:14:58.750 --> 00:14:58.760
it'—well,

00:14:58.760 --> 00:15:02.310
just do it. Whatever He says to

00:15:02.320 --> 00:15:04.949
do, do it.

00:15:04.959 --> 00:15:08.269
Even if it's a can—if He says, 'Billy

00:15:08.279 --> 00:15:11.269
Joe, I want you to go down to the

00:15:11.279 --> 00:15:13.670
Walmart store and buy five cans

00:15:13.680 --> 00:15:15.230
of green

00:15:15.230 --> 00:15:15.240
beans,'okay,

00:15:15.240 --> 00:15:18.949
go do it. And then all of

00:15:18.959 --> 00:15:20.710
a sudden, you go in your cupboard and

00:15:20.720 --> 00:15:22.629
you put those green beans inside

00:15:22.629 --> 00:15:22.639
there—those

00:15:22.639 --> 00:15:24.949
five cans—and you open it up

00:15:24.959 --> 00:15:28.310
the next day and there's thirty cans. He's

00:15:28.320 --> 00:15:30.430
the God of

00:15:30.440 --> 00:15:32.710
multiplication. He

00:15:32.720 --> 00:15:34.310
will be the God of the fishes and the

00:15:34.320 --> 00:15:35.629
loaves to

00:15:35.639 --> 00:15:38.230
you. Well, I only have enough for five

00:15:38.240 --> 00:15:40.269
cans. It

00:15:40.269 --> 00:15:40.279
doesn't

00:15:40.279 --> 00:15:42.790
matter. He had enough

00:15:42.800 --> 00:15:44.629
to turn the fishes and the loaves

00:15:44.639 --> 00:15:46.829
and multiply and feed

00:15:46.839 --> 00:15:49.030
thousands. How much more can He do it

00:15:49.040 --> 00:15:49.949
for

00:15:49.959 --> 00:15:53.350
you? I refuse to get in fear over all

00:15:53.360 --> 00:15:56.550
the end-time stuff. I refuse to let the

00:15:56.560 --> 00:15:58.430
circumstances of staying

00:15:58.440 --> 00:16:00.790
horizontal, looking at things going,

00:16:00.800 --> 00:16:02.310
'Man, what are we going to

00:16:02.320 --> 00:16:03.430
do?'and

00:16:03.440 --> 00:16:06.310
say, 'No, I take the care out

00:16:06.320 --> 00:16:09.430
of my prayer and I put my eyes on Jesus

00:16:09.440 --> 00:16:11.749
regardless of how much I have

00:16:11.759 --> 00:16:14.790
in my cupboard or my pantry or whatever

00:16:14.800 --> 00:16:17.189
I've got in my bank account.'If I've got

00:16:17.199 --> 00:16:19.749
$500 in there and I go, 'Man, all I've

00:16:19.759 --> 00:16:22.310
got is $500,'God is a God of

00:16:22.320 --> 00:16:24.870
multiplication. I told you the stories

00:16:24.880 --> 00:16:27.910
that I have that God takes a little

00:16:27.920 --> 00:16:30.629
bit of nothing and turns it into the

00:16:30.639 --> 00:16:32.069
fishes and the loaves and we're able to

00:16:32.079 --> 00:16:33.430
pay our bills for the whole month with

00:16:33.440 --> 00:16:36.150
eBay and Poshmark.

00:16:36.160 --> 00:16:37.710
We'll get down and we'll

00:16:37.720 --> 00:16:39.230
go,

00:16:39.240 --> 00:16:42.629
'Well, what are we going to

00:16:42.629 --> 00:16:42.639
do?'Trust

00:16:42.639 --> 00:16:46.629
God. Trust God. And that's

00:16:46.639 --> 00:16:50.310
what we've done over and over and over

00:16:50.320 --> 00:16:53.749
and He always comes

00:16:53.759 --> 00:16:56.470
through. I look back at my

00:16:56.470 --> 00:16:56.480
kids'videos

00:16:56.480 --> 00:16:59.269
even tonight of what we

00:16:59.279 --> 00:17:01.189
were like ten years ago

00:17:01.199 --> 00:17:04.829
when Braden

00:17:04.829 --> 00:17:04.839
was

00:17:04.839 --> 00:17:08.630
little, and I wasted so much

00:17:08.640 --> 00:17:11.029
time worrying and fretting about how I

00:17:11.039 --> 00:17:13.350
was going to make the electric, how I

00:17:13.360 --> 00:17:15.270
was going to pay the water bill, how I

00:17:15.280 --> 00:17:16.870
was going to pay the gas, how I was

00:17:16.880 --> 00:17:19.110
going to make my car payment.

00:17:19.120 --> 00:17:22.069
I worried so much as a father that it ate

00:17:22.079 --> 00:17:25.350
me up and drove me always

00:17:25.360 --> 00:17:27.429
to be in that state of care and

00:17:27.439 --> 00:17:29.830
that state of worry every single

00:17:29.840 --> 00:17:32.230
day that it robbed me of their childhood

00:17:32.240 --> 00:17:34.150
because I wasn't able just to sit back

00:17:34.160 --> 00:17:37.110
and relax because I was always thinking,

00:17:37.120 --> 00:17:39.350
'How am I going to take care of all these

00:17:39.360 --> 00:17:41.510
kids? How am I going to take care of

00:17:41.520 --> 00:17:43.830
this wife? I don't have an education. I

00:17:43.840 --> 00:17:45.270
don't have all this. What are You going

00:17:45.280 --> 00:17:47.669
to do for me, Lord?'Oh God, how are you

00:17:47.679 --> 00:17:50.230
going to take care of me? That

00:17:50.230 --> 00:17:50.240
was

00:17:50.240 --> 00:17:51.990
the way it was. When

00:17:52.000 --> 00:17:54.070
Megan was diagnosed and through all the

00:17:54.080 --> 00:17:56.310
things we’ve had going on, I

00:17:56.310 --> 00:17:56.320
said,

00:17:56.320 --> 00:17:57.990
'Lord, how are you going to

00:17:58.000 --> 00:18:00.470
do

00:18:00.470 --> 00:18:00.480
this?'But

00:18:00.480 --> 00:18:04.470
God has always provided. It may not have

00:18:04.480 --> 00:18:06.230
been as much as I thought I should

00:18:06.240 --> 00:18:08.789
have, but he always took care of us.

00:18:08.799 --> 00:18:12.310
Even if it wasn't what I really wanted

00:18:12.310 --> 00:18:12.320
or

00:18:12.320 --> 00:18:15.510
I

00:18:15.520 --> 00:18:17.909
didn't get to wear what I wanted, he

00:18:17.919 --> 00:18:20.990
always took care of

00:18:21.000 --> 00:18:23.669
me. It was just a simple act of

00:18:23.679 --> 00:18:26.630
trusting. I remember the days

00:18:26.630 --> 00:18:26.640
when

00:18:26.640 --> 00:18:29.750
I told you I

00:18:29.750 --> 00:18:29.760
was

00:18:29.760 --> 00:18:31.909
excited to find shoes at

00:18:31.909 --> 00:18:31.919
Payless

00:18:31.919 --> 00:18:35.870
for the kids. You just have to be

00:18:35.880 --> 00:18:39.110
thankful and walk in the thanksgiving

00:18:39.110 --> 00:18:39.120
for

00:18:39.120 --> 00:18:42.070
what he has provided. As you walk in

00:18:42.080 --> 00:18:45.110
thanksgiving and give him glory for

00:18:45.120 --> 00:18:47.510
everything he has done, he shows up and

00:18:47.520 --> 00:18:50.390
shows off with more. I believe

00:18:50.400 --> 00:18:51.830
that's where

00:18:51.840 --> 00:18:53.350
we are. People

00:18:53.350 --> 00:18:53.360
ask,

00:18:53.360 --> 00:18:55.110
'Where are you at, Brandon?'That’s where

00:18:55.110 --> 00:18:55.120
I’m

00:18:55.120 --> 00:18:57.750
at. I

00:18:57.760 --> 00:19:00.870
trust God, I stay vertical, and

00:19:00.880 --> 00:19:04.230
whatever he says to do, do it. Just

00:19:04.240 --> 00:19:08.630
like Mary

00:19:08.640 --> 00:19:10.830
said,

00:19:10.840 --> 00:19:13.909
'Whatever he says to do, do

00:19:13.909 --> 00:19:13.919
it.'In

00:19:13.919 --> 00:19:17.110
closing, people said,

00:19:17.120 --> 00:19:20.470
'I thought you saw Kim Jong-un removed.

00:19:20.480 --> 00:19:22.710
I thought you said in your last

00:19:22.720 --> 00:19:24.549
vision you saw a bomb going off

00:19:24.559 --> 00:19:28.710
on the border.'Yes, I did.

00:19:28.720 --> 00:19:30.470
Kim Jong-un was trying to be

00:19:30.470 --> 00:19:30.480
buddy-buddy

00:19:30.480 --> 00:19:33.190
with China and

00:19:33.200 --> 00:19:35.990
Russia. They were trying to bring

00:19:36.000 --> 00:19:40.270
South Korea into the pact by

00:19:40.280 --> 00:19:42.430
influencing their

00:19:42.440 --> 00:19:46.150
government and taking Taiwan back,

00:19:46.160 --> 00:19:49.190
making a

00:19:49.190 --> 00:19:49.200
stronger

00:19:49.200 --> 00:19:51.430
front for China because they're

00:19:51.440 --> 00:19:53.510
desperate. People say, 'You said you saw Kim

00:19:53.520 --> 00:19:55.669
Jong-un be removed. What

00:19:55.679 --> 00:19:56.870
happened with

00:19:56.870 --> 00:19:56.880
that?'I

00:19:56.880 --> 00:20:00.150
believe God

00:20:00.160 --> 00:20:03.510
is going to give an opportunity for

00:20:03.520 --> 00:20:06.549
the North Korean people to find him,

00:20:06.549 --> 00:20:06.559
so

00:20:06.559 --> 00:20:08.230
they

00:20:08.230 --> 00:20:08.240
don't

00:20:08.240 --> 00:20:09.830
all go to hell because they never heard

00:20:09.840 --> 00:20:14.070
the gospel. I believe God

00:20:14.080 --> 00:20:17.110
is just and he will bring

00:20:17.120 --> 00:20:21.549
justice to the

00:20:21.549 --> 00:20:21.559
injustice,

00:20:21.559 --> 00:20:25.029
and he will expose and remove

00:20:25.039 --> 00:20:28.630
Kim Jong-un one day. He will do

00:20:28.630 --> 00:20:28.640
the same with

00:20:28.640 --> 00:20:31.990
his sister. Just

00:20:32.000 --> 00:20:34.789
like he did with Pharaoh, he will lead

00:20:34.799 --> 00:20:38.789
his people out of bondage again

00:20:38.799 --> 00:20:41.590
and give them a time

00:20:41.600 --> 00:20:44.070
to hear what the

00:20:44.080 --> 00:20:46.149
Spirit of the Lord is saying.

00:20:46.159 --> 00:20:47.669
People may not agree, but I

00:20:47.669 --> 00:20:47.679
believe

00:20:47.679 --> 00:20:50.990
God is a God of

00:20:51.000 --> 00:20:53.430
mercy. We are running

00:20:53.440 --> 00:20:55.830
out of time and coming to

00:20:55.840 --> 00:20:57.510
the end of things. You

00:20:57.510 --> 00:20:57.520
ask,

00:20:57.520 --> 00:20:59.310
'What did you think about the eclipse,

00:20:59.310 --> 00:20:59.320
Brandon?'I

00:20:59.320 --> 00:21:01.950
believe it's more than

00:21:01.960 --> 00:21:04.470
finances. I get caught up in

00:21:04.480 --> 00:21:06.310
what I say; I’m not the

00:21:06.320 --> 00:21:07.549
best

00:21:07.559 --> 00:21:10.789
speaker. I go over these videos

00:21:10.789 --> 00:21:10.799
many

00:21:10.799 --> 00:21:13.070
times in my mind

00:21:13.070 --> 00:21:13.080
beforehand

00:21:13.080 --> 00:21:16.070
because people

00:21:16.080 --> 00:21:19.270
are mean to me and I try

00:21:19.280 --> 00:21:21.909
hard to say the right things.

00:21:21.909 --> 00:21:21.919
As

00:21:21.919 --> 00:21:24.789
I said, I try with the words.

00:21:24.799 --> 00:21:26.390
Diana often says, 'You meant to say

00:21:26.400 --> 00:21:27.990
this,

00:21:27.990 --> 00:21:28.000
Brandon,'when

00:21:28.000 --> 00:21:29.270
she's sitting next to me. She

00:21:29.270 --> 00:21:29.280
doesn't

00:21:29.280 --> 00:21:30.310
want to interrupt

00:21:30.310 --> 00:21:30.320
my

00:21:30.320 --> 00:21:33.110
flow, but I’d rather she did because

00:21:33.120 --> 00:21:35.590
I say certain words while meaning

00:21:35.590 --> 00:21:35.600
something else. In

00:21:35.600 --> 00:21:37.750
my mind, it’s right,

00:21:37.760 --> 00:21:39.830
but it comes out

00:21:39.830 --> 00:21:39.840
differently.

00:21:39.840 --> 00:21:42.310
That’s

00:21:42.320 --> 00:21:43.590
when people say, 'Well, you

00:21:43.600 --> 00:21:45.590
said this,'and I

00:21:45.590 --> 00:21:45.600
realize I didn’t

00:21:45.600 --> 00:21:47.830
mean it that way.

00:21:47.840 --> 00:21:52.230
If you

00:21:52.240 --> 00:21:55.430
truly knew me, you'd know I try really

00:21:55.440 --> 00:21:57.990
hard.

00:21:58.000 --> 00:22:00.549
I'll say it again, and I

00:22:00.559 --> 00:22:02.470
hope my son helps

00:22:02.470 --> 00:22:02.480
me. I’ve

00:22:02.480 --> 00:22:04.710
told him, 'Please

00:22:04.720 --> 00:22:06.310
correct me if I mess

00:22:06.320 --> 00:22:09.029
up.'What

00:22:09.039 --> 00:22:12.870
I saw regarding the eclipse

00:22:14.559 --> 00:22:17.990
in April

00:22:18.000 --> 00:22:20.149
happened a year ago.

00:22:20.159 --> 00:22:22.630
That

00:22:22.640 --> 00:22:26.070
Tuesday, yesterday,

00:22:26.080 --> 00:22:27.990
was part of a window of opportunity

00:22:27.990 --> 00:22:28.000
for

00:22:28.000 --> 00:22:30.630
the shifting of

00:22:30.640 --> 00:22:33.510
finances. He said, 'Pay attention to Israel and Iran

00:22:33.510 --> 00:22:33.520
in the days ahead.'This

00:22:33.520 --> 00:22:35.750
is the part I left out.

00:22:45.919 --> 00:22:47.430
People say, 'You messed up on

